Propagation Notes
-------------------

 - Plant Type: Vine
 - Propagation: Seed
 - Hardiness:  frost tender
 - Flowering Season:  mid summer

Easy to grow from seed
Likes well-drained garden soil, in full sun
Quickly grows to cover an arch or obelisk
Flowers from summer to autumn

2024-05-15:  Bought this plant in desperation to get something growing on the obelisk as the snails continues to decimate the sweetpeas
2024-10-06:  Although a very common plant and invasive is some regions in the world, this is an easy growing plant with lots of colour throughout the season.